outh]]'''\n!style=\"background:#9f9;\"|32.3%\n!style=\"background:#9f9;\"|29.8%\n!style=\"background:#9f9;\"|26.9%\n!style=\"background:#9f9;\"|24.7%\n!style=\"background:#9f9;\"|23.8%\n!style=\"background:#9f9;\"|21.7%\n!style=\"background:#9f9;\"|20.6%\n!style=\"background:#9f9;\"|19.1%\n!style=\"background:#9f9;\"|18.6%\n!style=\"background:#9f9;\"|18.5%\n!style=\"background:#9f9;\"|18.9%\n!style=\"background:#9f9;\"|19.2%\n!style=\"background:#9f9;\"|-13.1%\n|-\n|style=\"background:#9f9;\"|'''[[Western United States|West]]'''\n!style=\"background:#9f9;\"|0.7%\n!style=\"background:#9f9;\"|0.7%\n!style=\"background:#9f9;\"|0.9%\n!style=\"background:#9f9;\"|1.0%\n!style=\"background:#9f9;\"|1.2%\n!style=\"background:#9f9;\"|2.9%\n!style=\"background:#9f9;\"|3.9%\n!style=\"background:#9f9;\"|4.9%\n!style=\"background:#9f9;\"|5.2%\n!style=\"background:#9f9;\"|5.4%\n!style=\"background:#9f9;\"|4.9%\n!style=\"background:#9f9;\"|4.8%\n!style=\"background:#9f9;\"|+4.1%\n|-\n|}\n\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|+African Americans as a Percentage of the Total Population By U.S. State (1900\u20132010)<ref name=\"auto\" /><ref name=\"pitt.edu\" /><ref name=\"census.gov\" />\n|-\n!State||[[List of regions of the United States|Region]]||1900||1910||1920||1930||1940||1950||1960||1970||1980||1990||2000||2010||Change in the Black Percentage of the Total Population Between 1900 and 2010<br />\n|-\n|style=\"background:#9bddff;\"|'''{{Flagdeco|United States|size=23px}}&nbsp;[[United States]]'''\n!style=\"background:#9bddff;\"|N/A\n!style=\"background:#9bddff;\"|11.6%\n!style=\"background:#9bddff;\"|10.7%\n!style=\"background:#9bddff;\"|9.9%\n!style=\"background:#9bddff;\"|9.7%\n!style=\"background:#9bddff;\"|9.8%\n!style=\"background:#9bddff;\"|10.0%\n!style=\"background:#9bddff;\"|10.5%\n!style=\"background:#9bddff;\"|11.1%\n!style=\"background:#9bddff;\"|11.7%\n!style=\"background:#9bddff;\"|12.1%\n!style=\"background:#9bddff;\"|12.3%\n!style=\"background:#9bddff;\"|12.6%\n!styl